title: Ecology: Pragmatism & Local Activism (vegan / vegans / veganism)
description: A recurring issue on the channel is the contrast between local (community-based) activism and more "nomadic" approaches to social change.  In this video I'm speaking with Adriane Gilbert, a vegan activist from Southern Ontario.  At the time of the interview, she was 18 years old and had been vegan for less than a year.  You can find her on instagram, here: https://www.instagram.com/adriane__gilbert/
